features: ✅ Innovative Thermal Softening Process: These diapers utilize a cutting-edge hot air technique to thermally soften fibers, enhancing their fluffiness and softness. This process guarantees superior comfort and air permeability, safeguarding your baby's sensitive skin from irritation during extended usage.

✅ Luxurious Cotton-Velvet Fusion: Crafted with a blend of cotton and velvety materials, these diapers are designed with an ultra-light 0.8D fabric density and 10-micron fibers. This delicate composition helps reduce skin irritation and allergy risks, ensuring a soft, comforting embrace for newborns.

✅ Eco-Sensitive Hypoallergenic Construction: Made with FSC-certified, highly absorbent wood pulp, these diapers are devoid of harmful chemicals like additives, parabens, chlorine, fragrances, and bleach. Sourced from five countries and rigorously tested through nine procedures, they are tailored to effectively safeguard against allergies.

✅ Enhanced Comfort with Reduced Friction: Featuring a unique embossed pattern on the top layer, these diapers reduce skin contact by 45%, thus diminishing friction. This design ensures that each movement is soothingly gentle on your baby's skin.

✅ Superior Absorption for Ultimate Dryness: Engineered for swift absorption within 10 seconds and equipped with over a million tiny ventilation holes, these diapers maintain excellent dryness. This quality is crucial in preventing discomfort caused by moisture and rashes, ensuring a tranquil sleep for both the infant and the parent.

reviews.reviewText: I’m really impressed with these diapers. They are super thin yet very absorbent. They seem to fit well, and my daughter has not had any leaks using these! I would definitely purchase again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars gentle for baby's skin
reviews.reviewText: The diapers' composition, a fusion of cotton and velvety materials offers a gentle embrace for newborns. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very soft and thin
reviews.reviewText: We are foster parents and try to keep a variety of diapers on-hand to accommodate different needs. These are very soft and thin. They are so nice for babies who have sensitive skin, as they are hypoallergenic. Sensitive babies have not had skin problems with these diapers. They are pricey, however.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So light and perfect!
reviews.reviewText: I love these diapers!!! I had no clue what to expect, but my baby has sensitive skin and these really work well for us. The material is thin and soft, but held up well overnight for my 4 month old. I haven’t seen any rash or irritation on my little one.However, one thing to consider when choosing diapers for young infants is the potential for blowouts. There isn’t a flap on the back of these to protect from poo explosions (the name brand we were previously using has them and they have saved us) and we were about a centimeter away from a full outfit change this morning.Additionally, the cost of these diapers are a bit too pricey for us to continue using them at the moment, sadly. And the cost per diaper seems to increase as you go up a size for less diapers, which I found odd. However, these are well made and if I had the extra funds I would have loved to purchase more!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Soft and Comfortable, but Moderate Absorbency and Blowout Protection
reviews.reviewText: I have tried several diaper brands, and I find these to be just okay. Although these diapers are lightweight and made of soft materials, they only offer moderate absorbency and blowout protection. They do contour well to my baby's body, which is a plus. However, I have had better experiences with other diaper brands that are also more affordable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Just OK, but wouldn’t get again.
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to love these, but unfortunately they just aren’t the best, especially with the price tag. They aren’t the best fitting, as they are too flimsy and resulted in a few bad blowouts and leaks that other diapers would have prevented. They aren’t the easiest to put on, nor the best fit. The price point just isn’t up to par with the quality of the diapers, and I wanted to love them as they are cute but not functional which is most important for my baby’s needs. The sizing is a bit off, and as much as they may be cute and cute packaging, I’d rather stick with other brands that are similar to this but reassure the needs and best fit for baby. Can’t say I’d recommend these, but the fact that they are hypoallergenic is a plus but there are better ones out there that also are as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Decent, but not very diarrhea friendly
reviews.reviewText: These diapers are decent enough for most every day use. We still use a specific overnight diaper because our toddler is a heavy wetter when he sleeps, so we've been using these during daytime.They do alright 90% of the time, but twice he had diarrhea and it leaked out of the sides. It wasn't even blow-out level; liquidy, but a small amount so I would expect the diaper to contain it. They are super soft and comfortable for him, so we'll finish the pack but maybe use our overnights if he's got an upset stomach.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: OK so like. These seem like a premium alternative to common national brands. They seem thinner, softer and more absorbent. But the cost seems really quite high. They do fit well.I feel like it might be the difference between a Lexus and a Toyota.I definitely don't have any strong complaints, but I feel like I wouldn't go out of my way to get these again.Like I said: Fit super well.
